name: GROSS MUGSHOT #10
description: This collection gathers the most offensive mugshots from the most unlovely extraterrestrial felons and culprits. Taken and distributed by the Spatial Authorities. MUGSHOT#10 -  (放浪者金星ヤギ - Wanderer Venus Goat) This cutie was arrested and charged for multiple violent robbery on the highways all around the galaxy. He convinces the passengers from other spaceships about fake damage or troubles on the engine, and when they hop off the ship, he jumps in and takes all stuff from the victims. Be aware on the road!
